&lt;li&gt;Fully support all post printing operations. Includes but not limited to: powder removal, support removal, borescope and other inspections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Always ensure procedures are followed to ensure safety and to deliver defect free hardware&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep a clean, organized, and thoroughly maintained work space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure product quality and conformance to specifications and/or engineering requirements&lt;/li&gt;
