&lt;li&gt;Operate post processing equipment such as drills, handheld grinders and CNC machines as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to flex support other areas of the Additive or Raptor organization to assist areas in need&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to adapt with process change and updates to work instructions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
