&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI to discover and fix security issues in Starshield infrastructure and systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance and perform testing of AI integrations into new and existing Starshield systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify new areas of the program where meaningful security improvements can be gained via automation and AI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain existing production systems and improve security posture via both direct implementation and recommendations to other teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
