&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design of antennas for communications and sensors, in VHF through Ka-band&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and characterization of antenna, feed, and front-end prototypes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-uuid=&quot;cc6b27f6-df42-4770-8b35-974fa8dae826&quot;&gt;Development of measurement systems to support design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-uuid=&quot;76d4842b-1338-4658-96b1-6d6f89d7105a&quot;&gt;Analysis of wireless systems (antenna isolation, patterns with large structures, propagation effects, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multidisciplinary collaboration to improve RF manufacturing, mechanical integration, and testability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
