&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in an engineering discipline&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of relevant professional or project experience with antennas or RF systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of experience with 3D electromagnetic simulation tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
